INTRODUCTION\par
\par
The last decade has seen Mario's threat to Bowser's dictatorship wane, and the fragile but somehow lasting peace has seen the Koopalings through adolescence and into young adulthood. As they are no longer occupied by assaults on their father's kingdom nor sharing in the responsibility to defend it, their lives have become steeped in the drama and obstacles that befall any normal, quickly maturing family. And though Mario cannot sit back forever as Bowser's power and influence continue to grow, he nonetheless remains in retreat as the Koopalings' lives are guided, albeit crookedly, by their own individual circumstances, and the gentle but unyielding pull of destiny.\par
\par
